  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 140°C/ 120°C (fan)/ gas 1</p><p>Add your <strong>shredded kale</strong> to a large baking tray with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up, then put the tray in the oven for 25-30 min or until crispy – this is your <strong>crispy kale</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/southern-style-butter-bean-and-bacon-soup-with-crispy-kale/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a medium sized pot over a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>bacon lardons</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/southern-style-butter-bean-and-bacon-soup-with-crispy-kale/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Top, tail, peel and dice your <strong>carrot[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>leek[s]</strong> in half lengthways, wash thoroughly to remove any grit then top, tail and slice finely</p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>butter beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/southern-style-butter-bean-and-bacon-soup-with-crispy-kale/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the bacon is golden, add the <strong>sliced leek</strong> and <strong>diced carrot</strong> to the pot with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to soften</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> and <strong>soft cheese</strong> with 700ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[1.1L]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.4L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>creamy stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/southern-style-butter-bean-and-bacon-soup-with-crispy-kale/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have softened, add <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), <strong>drained butter beans</strong>, <strong>dried thyme</strong>, <strong>bay leaf[ves]</strong>, most of your <strong>southern fried seasoning </strong>(save some for garnish!) and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/southern-style-butter-bean-and-bacon-soup-with-crispy-kale/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>creamy stock </strong>with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 8-10 min or until the vegetables are tender and the stock has thickened slightly – this is your <strong>southern-style butter bean & bacon soup</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/southern-style-butter-bean-and-bacon-soup-with-crispy-kale/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>remaining chopped garlic </strong>to a small bowl with 20g <span class=\"text-purple\">[30g] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[40g]</span> <strong>butter </strong>and mix until fully combined – this is your <strong>garlic butter</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half and place in the <strong>toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until toasted</p><p>Spread the <strong>toasted ciabatta </strong>with the <strong>garlic butter </strong>and slice in half – these are your <strong>garlic toasts</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/southern-style-butter-bean-and-bacon-soup-with-crispy-kale/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>southern-style butter bean & bacon soup </strong>in bowls and top with the <strong>crispy kale</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>garlic toasts </strong>to the side and sprinkle the kale with the <strong>remaining southern fried seasoning</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
  ],
